Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Button
    This class represents a single button that has a boolean value.
    DevVars
    This class contains static boolean variables used to disable and enable certain aspects of code.
    FloatButton
    An instance class represents a button which value is stored as a float.
    HardwareLightbot
    This hardware class is for LightBot, the new robot.
    HardwareSPQR
    This class defines all hardware on the robot.
    Input
    This class manages input abstractions.
    LightbotMainOpMode
    This is the main opmode used for Lightbot in the driver-controlled period.
    MainOpMode
    This is the main opmode used in the driver-controlled period.
    RRWSP
    This OpMode starts from the right-most red starting point against the wall, with the wobble goal loaded on the intake drop.
    ShutdownTFOD
    This class simply allows multithreading to shutdown TensorFlow object detection asynchronously.
    SPQRLinearOpMode
    Custom Linear OpMode class with extra functions.
    TestOpMode
    This OpMode is used for development and should NOT be used in game.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Buttons
    This enumeration defines the buttons on a gamepad that are booleans.
    FloatButtons
    This enumeration defines the buttons on a gamepad that are represented by floats.
    Rings
    How many rings there are in the stack.
